Install the following to get the game working:

    liballegro2.4
    liballegro2.4-dev

 System reference~

main modules folders:

	./system # gameSystem module
	./video  # gameVideo  module
	./brain  # gameBrain  module

auxiliary folders:

	./util    # utilitary headers
	./modules # extern modules (almost all)
	./libs    # extern libs
